Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたち４５組は\N正規の給料を取り返すため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:14.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and the 45s, to win back their proper salaries, band together in shared sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:14.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忍耐の３ヵ月を共にしのぐと宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:18.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Losers among losers, men trapped at the bottom of the abyss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負け組の中の負け組\Nどん底の男たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:21.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打倒大槻のために今 立ち上がる！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:21.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,they now stand forth to overthrow Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:24.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,500)\pos(640,505)}Abuse and Endurance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つために！\N生まれ変わるために！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:29.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨てた！惰性の安息を！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They abandon their habitual respites!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:34.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐える！飲み食いしている\N仲間を尻目に 耐える！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:34.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endure the suspicious glares from their comrades who partake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:38.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Four for each of us, one peanut a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:37.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人４個ずつだ\Nただしピーナッツは１つずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:38.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,基本的に金はカイジが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In general, Kaiji handles the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タバコは前田が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maeda the cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and Miyoshi the candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,甘い物は三好が管理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:52.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They survive sharing their meager rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少ないブツを\N互いに分け合って暮らす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:55.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, gambling and drinking are forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 バクチ 酒は御法度！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:04.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連中 結束してクリアする気ですよ\N給料前借り生活を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:04.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like they think they can pay back their advances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:08.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 続かない続かない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll never hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に続いたって\Nこいつで殺せば それまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:13.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if they do, I'll finish them off with these dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プハー　フフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 看護当番の日のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's turn to attend to the ill arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:31.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're Kaiji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた カイジさんだろ？\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:36.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(咳)\Nエスポワール 生き残り組の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:37.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji Ito, the one who survived the {\i1}Espoir{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伊藤カイジ\Nああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:38.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:44.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう伝え聞いて\N話がしたいと思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:43.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I have something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は石田広光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:45.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Hiromitsu Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:50.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたに船で世話になった\N石田光司の息子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:50.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The son of Koji Ishida, who you saved on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:02:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ そういえば面影ある！\Nあるある！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:01:59.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へー こんな大きな息子さんが\Nいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never thought his son would be this big already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっくりだなー 石田さんに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You look just like your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:13.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 笑っただろ　腹ん中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're laughing at me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\N親子揃って落ちぶれてやがるって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:17.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Laughing at how I've fucked up just as bad as my father did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と… とんでもない！何を急に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! Why are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:24.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be that much like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:25.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれほど親父のようには\Nなりたくなかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:35.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ 奴がちゃんとしていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:32.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:38.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he had straightened out, I never would have ended up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなとこに落ちることは\Nなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:41.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなとこに… こんなとこに\Nこんなとこに！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never ever would have ended up in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 肩代わりしたのか？\N親父さんの借金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:49.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So you inherited your father's debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:53.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！何で俺がそんなこと\Nしなきゃいけねえんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:53.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! Why would I get stuck with that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃない　俺の借金は300！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme a fucking break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My debt is three million!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\N借金は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:02.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I went into debt gambling... And then this and that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のバクチとか あと色々…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったらここに落ちたのは お前の\N責任じゃねえの？どう考えても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:07.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So really, it's your own fault you're down here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う 分かってない\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My debt is three million! Just three million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の借金は300！\Nたかだか300万なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:18.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぐらいの はした金\N払うだろ普通 親なら！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally I could just get that from my parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに奴ときたら 泣きそうな顔を\Nするだけで何もできない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But when I asked him, all he did was sit there looking like he was about to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくしたら何とかするって\Nおん出て それっきりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He said to wait and he'd try to do something, and that was it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… それっていつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:28.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When was—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:33.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？船から戻って\Nしばらくしてからだから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting since right after he came back from the ship, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,去年の７月頃だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:35.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Around last July.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then... He must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:39.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか やっぱり！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:43.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの橋で死んだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He must have died on that girder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時 石田さんは\N懸命に精算しようとしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He was trying his hardest to clear his debts then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とかしたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He wanted to help out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not just with his own debts, but with his son's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:53.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の借金 そして息子の借金を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:57.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった300万ぽっち\N払えよ それくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:57.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's only three mil! Just fuckin' pay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even going to college would have been cheaper compared to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大学に行ったことを考えりゃ\N安いもんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:04.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Dammit dammit dammit dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ！クソ クソ クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと奴みたいには\Nなるまいと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:07.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I told myself I wouldn't end up like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキの頃から ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに気づいたら\N風体からダメさ加減まで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:16.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you're laughing at me because I look just like him and I'm as much of a failure as he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっくりだってんだから\N笑わせやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… まるで呪いだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:22.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a curse... A terrible curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タチの悪い呪い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しやがる！\Nバカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just like your dad? Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:40.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と親父さんがそっくりだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,笑わせるな！\Nまるで違うじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:46.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're scum! You blame everyone else for your problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:47.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は何でもかんでも\N他人のせいにする クズ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親父さんは そんな人間じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your father wasn't that kind of man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:54.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He accepted his weakness, his failures, and kept fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の弱さ ダメさ加減を\N全部 受け入れて戦ってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！別物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So don't give me that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで別物だ　話にならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not even worth mentioning in the same breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:14.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやー わしも色々\N男を見てきたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:16.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've known a lot of men, but Kaiji is the best among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピカイチは カイジ君だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん カイジ君　彼は大物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ 何が大物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean, real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:27.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He looks like just an ordinary guy, but I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パッと見は平凡な男だけど\N何というか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:31.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は逆境に\N強いっていうかさ 諦めないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When the chips are down, he's the one you want on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He never gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:35.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter what depths of despair he finds himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえそれが\Nどんな絶望的な状況でも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:44.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１週間後 石田の息子 広光は\N現場に復帰していた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:44.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ishida's son Hiromitsu returns to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:48.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He had overworked himself momentarily in order to secure a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:48.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は疲労がたまると仮病を使い\N病棟で休んでいたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが彼のここでの\Nしのぎ方だった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is how he survives here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 奴はＥ班の借金組で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:06:00.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've heard he's one of the debtors of E Team,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その借金を無理やり返そうと\N仲間と無給で頑張ってるらしいが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:05.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and he's fasting with his friends to pay those loans off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何それ？大バカじゃん\Nできるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That'll never work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:15.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなマネしたら 金を貸している\NＥ班の班長の気分を害するだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:14.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that's going to do is piss off the E Team foreman who lent them the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:16.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親父は何も分かってない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:24.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Worshiping that idiot like a hero? My dad didn't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなバカを\N英雄視してるんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コラ！何だお前たちは？\Nそれでシャワー浴びたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you all? You call that showering!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,汗臭いぞ\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You smell like mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ それじゃ　やり直せ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No good! Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and the others reluctantly return to the showers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちは\N渋々 シャワー室へ行き
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then, twenty minutes later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:44.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして20分後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの 俺たちの食事は？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:50.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Um, where's our food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの あるか\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You expect food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅いんだよ お前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:07:01.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're late, and the rules here are that you don't get food if you're late to dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:59.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの規則で 所定の時間内に\N着席できなかった者には
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食事させないことになってるんだ\Nクッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:12.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiots! If they give the higher-ups trouble, of course they're going to get this kind of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが　上に逆らえば\Nこの手の嫌がらせは当然さ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 奴らが食事の時間に\N遅れてきまして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They came late for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:22.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん それはいかんともしがたいな\N規則だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, well. That's against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしどうかな\N正規の食事はダメでも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:29.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But even if they miss their meal, why can't they stay for ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:28.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらが特注した料理なら\N構わないんじゃないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nこれは帝愛グループの縛りの外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:34.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This doesn't come from the Teiai Group. It's entirely our own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう わしらのものなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ それでしたら…\Nだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about it, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだね カイジ君\Nここはひとつ 我々と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Care to share a meal with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give them one taste of luxury,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜいたくを一度 味わわせて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:50.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倹約節制の糸を切ろうって魂胆\N陥落へのゆさぶり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:50.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and they'll abandon their frugality and fall back into their old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見え見えだけど うまいんだよな\Nあの班長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious, but he's got great delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:57.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その切り札を出すﾀｲﾐﾝｸﾞというか\N持っていき方がさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:57.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Playing a card like that is all in the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいやいや すまなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:05.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm sorry about the shower thing, but let's let bygones be bygones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャワーの一件は謝るよ\Nまっ 勘弁してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっ 座って座って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now go ahead! Sit right down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たまには肉も食わんとな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Man can't live on bread alone, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに こいつも\Nずいぶん やってないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:14.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And how long has it been since you've had a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:19.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C'mon, chug it right down! There's plenty more where it came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっ グーッとやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーッと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくが 金なんかねえぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You do know I can't afford this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I couldn't take money for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言ってるんだ\N金なんか取るもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is entirely out of my good will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは100パーセント\N善意のビールだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近 カイジ君\Nちょっとおかしかったろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've been acting funny lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしゃ ただそんなカイジ君と\N仲直りしたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:38.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I just want to make up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きにしていいってことだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So you're saying I can do whatever I want with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ああ もちろんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:47.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course! Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ いってくれ 一気に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぎゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 班長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:13.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The foreman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど… どうぞ\Nフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:18.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことだ　遠慮なく\N好きにさせてもらったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て コラ！\Nただで済むと思ってんのか 貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't think you'll get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許してやれよ 石和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Forgive him, Isawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I wasn't in any danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの身に\N危険が迫ったわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに万事穏便に済ませることが\N班長たる者の務めだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:04.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And it's a foreman's duty to make sure that things are settled quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし…\N考えてもみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:10.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, think about it. The company has this cafeteria under surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:10.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは常に組織側から\Nカメラで監視されてる食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:16.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somewhere with no cameras like the toilets or blind spots on the work site would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カメラの目が届かぬトイレや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現場の死角のような所なら\Nいざ知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:19.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で暴力沙汰など\Nできるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't be violent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:25.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は ここんとこ\N続けてた節制のストレスで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:28.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The stress of fasting like this must have made poor Kaiji have a breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,精神のバランスが崩れておるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:31.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He would never be so insolent otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でなければ\Nあんな無礼をする道理がない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:36.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は今 自分で自分が何を\Nしてるのかよく分かってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:36.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He simply doesn't understand what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or how it makes the other person involved feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その行為が相手に\Nどういう感情を生むかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:43.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに精神失調状態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's obviously having a mental breakdown. {->psychataxia}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:47.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 許してやろうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:47.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So we should let it slip, just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寛容な精神で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:51.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's only generous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ？フフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:02.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The foreman takes this moment to begin his bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:03.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを契機に班長大槻の\Nイジメが動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Devious bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陰湿なイジメ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キツくて危険な作業の割り当て
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Deliberately assigning the most dangerous jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の嫌がる時間外の病人の世話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The hated overtime hours nursing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴミ出し
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,KP duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:21.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに日常的 嫌がらせ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And daily harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:28.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pouring water over the sugar cubes which formed their rare luxuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:28.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジらの蓄え\N数少ない嗜好品の角砂糖が水浸し
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:32.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And dirty water! They were ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも汚水　台なしに！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:37.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして　どうして… ひどい…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:37.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why? Why!? This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,着替えには生ゴミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Garbage in their changes of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,靴は泥詰め！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Filling their boots with mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiots! They're total idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:12:00.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカだ　あいつは本当にバカだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:04.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長とぶつかるなんて\Nそんなことして何の得がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:04.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They can't fight the foreman! It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:34.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう許せない　こうなったら\Nみんなで班長を…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:34.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuck him! We need to kill him before he kills us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ　バカ言うな\Nだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop it. That's crazy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:41.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, Miyoshi. If anything, I need to thank the foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:41.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか 三好　俺は逆に\N感謝したいくらいなんだぜ 班長に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？\N奴は自分のやってることが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:47.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He doesn't realize what what he's doing will cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう結果を生むか\Nまるで分かってない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌がらせをすればするほど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:53.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Every trick he pulls just tightens the noose around his own neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は自分で自分の首を\N絞めてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I forgive him for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:58.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから これぐらいは\N許してやろうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's only generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寛容な精神で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And! And!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして そして待ちに待った\Nその日が来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The day they awaited arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:11.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,85 days after the day they decided! Two missed paydays after!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決起の日から85日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,途中 ２度あった給料日を\Nやり過ごし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:15.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちは\Nついにやり遂げたのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and the others have nearly accomplished their goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Complete payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:19.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全返済 借金生活の解消を！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An end to the debtor's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 今日は給料日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, today is payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３ヵ月ぶりの給料日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The first payday in three months!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズどもが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those losers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How did those losers pull it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてできるんだ？\Nあんなクズどもが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How could they endure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてあんな忍耐を…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanaka... Arikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:39.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,田中　有川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:42.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Awano... Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,淡野　服部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kitagawa... Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北川　高橋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:53.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:55.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚いたな　案外 ガマン強いんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never expected you to hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 今回のところは\N褒めといてやるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Congratulations are in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:02.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おめでとうよ カイジ君\N見直したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:01.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Good job, Kaiji. I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:04.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 何っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:12.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He finally receives it! His entire, ungarnished salary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:12.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに得る\Nピンハネされていない正規の給料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,92,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９万1000ペリカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:18.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コラ 失礼だぞ！\Nその場で改めるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing checking it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you trust us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信用してねえのか\N俺たちのことを！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:24.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりめえだろ！\N信用できるはずがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I could never trust you brutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鬼畜じゃねえか お前らは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:29.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're beasts who sacrifice your comrades for your own profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らは自分の利益のために\N仲間を犠牲にする鬼畜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone, check yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなも確認しろよ\N何と言われようと その場で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we're going to object, it's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once we leave this room, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度 離れたら\Nもうそれっきりだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい\Nお… おお…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:38.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このクソガキ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This shithead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:50.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男 黒崎義裕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This man, Yoshihiro Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:56.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川失脚後 帝愛グループ\Nナンバー２になった人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:54.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Became #2 in the Teiai Group after Tonegawa's failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男だろ？\Nはっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川を失脚させた野良犬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's the stray who brought down Tonegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人騒がせなカイジとかいう男は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji the troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　よくご存じですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I see you're already well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:13.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ 実は今日ここに来たのは\Nそれが楽しみでもあったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:12.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was hoping to see more of him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな男かと思ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of man he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しアップにしてくれるか？\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can you zoom in a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:23.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… なるほど野良犬だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Quite a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,典型的な野良犬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The very picture of a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし この地下に落ちても\Nまだ抜けていないようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:31.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But even having fallen so far, his fangs haven't come out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牙は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 大盆開帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the table opens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, all-comers underground chinchirorin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:44.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来 全班参加自由の\N地下チンチロは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:49.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,was set for the first and third Saturday of the month!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:49.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第１ 第３土曜の夜\N月２回開帳がここの決まり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:56.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But since this month has five Saturdays, there is a special night of gambling on payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 今月は第５土曜まである月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも\N給料日と重なるという特異日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:59.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A wild night which comes but a few times a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,年に数回 訪れる嵐の夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:04.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the best of times, such a night is wildly pivotal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:04.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなただでさえ物騒な\N大荒れ必至の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:10.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But tonight, a rumor gallops through the depths of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:08.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜 その嵐に拍車をかける\Nある噂 風評が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地下を巡っていた\Nまことしやかに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A rumor with the ring of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたち４５組が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:18.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That tonight is the night Kaiji and the 45s turn on the foremen's clique!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長グループに\N噛みつくであろうと！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:27.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか動かないな 連中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:27.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're not making their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with being cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:29.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが慎重になるのも無理はない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くに引けない勝負になって\N金の乗せ合いになったら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:35.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If it comes down to a battle of bankrolls, Ohtsuki has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的に大槻が有利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジらは６人全員集めても\N54万ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:40.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if Kaiji and the others put all their money together, they have 540,000 perica.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:46.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But as you know, Ohtsuki saves up his cut as a foreman for gambling money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが大槻は知っての通り
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長暮らしで\N莫大な金を蓄えている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I had to guess, I'd say he has at least a million perica.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:49.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少なく見積もって\N1000万ペリカはある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 50万なんて\Nゴミみたいなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Half a mil will lose to that any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:56.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その気になれば\Nあっという間に潰せる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can finish them off any time he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潰されてたまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I endured for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のために耐えてきたと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただタイミングが難しい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the timing is going to be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:08.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When to wait, and when to bet heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:08.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の持っていき方\Nバクチの導入のし方が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでしくじると…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I mess this up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:16.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All my savings, all my endurance, all my planning will be wiped away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで積み重ねてきた忍耐\N策略が全て水の泡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づかれたらダメだ\N俺たちの必勝の骨組み
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't let him figure out how we're going to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:28.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he gets a whiff of it, the door to {the gunpowder storage, our path to}victory closes tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのにおいを敵に気づかれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火薬庫の扉は閉ざされてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:31.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利への道が！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちから動くのは\N最小限にとどめなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to finish him with my first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait for him to make a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは奴に動いてもらうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:40.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが一番いい\Nそれが一番ナチュラル
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it. That will come off the most natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ来い
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちをまた４５組に\N落としたいんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You want to make us 45s again, don't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:49.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらにこの大ギャラリーの前で\N勝ちきり 誇示をしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:49.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You want to show off by beating us in front of this audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:53.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You want to show off your luck in front of everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己の勝負強さを見せつけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 満座の前で！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You want everyone to be jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲しいんだろ その羨望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その注目！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You want that attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いただき いただき
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I win, I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:16.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You know, I've had the feeling that someone rotten is watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かさっきから見とるのう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,性根の腐った奴が１人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隅っこで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:18.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,From the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\N来た
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:30.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… スカッと腹を決めたら\Nどうだね カイジ君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:30.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why don't you work up the guts to buy in, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしら もう対決するしかないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need to settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:36.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone's on edge waiting for our grudge match!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:36.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 声には出さねど期待しておる\N遺恨試合を！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろ？カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:48.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのかよ？\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:51.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When I join in, playtime's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が行くとなったら\N遊びじゃなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I want to see everything on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:56.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張らせてもらうぜ 限界を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:00.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ バカ！何を言い出すんだ！\Nそんなことしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:19:00.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's he saying!? If he does that—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界を超えて か…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはつまり\Nマックス２万の限定解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Meaning, the lifting of the 20,000 limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,青天井！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… バカなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:28.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が しかし どうしても\Nそれがご所望とあらば仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:28.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you want it that badly, I'm not going to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを受けるのも班長の務め
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:36.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's my duty as a foreman to accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに言わせたぞ その言葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you to say that in front of everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの前で！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの命を懸けた戦いが\N今 始まる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:17.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's life-or-death battle begins!
